title: Care Bears Coloring Book - Hugs and Kisses
description: 59 black-and-white images taken from the coloring book "Hugs and Kisses." Scanned at 300 dpi. Each image is about 600k. Only the coloring book images have been included as opposed to the "activity" pages, which were rather inane tasks such as circling objects or descrambling the names of different bears. The pictures are ready to be printed on 8.5" x 8" pages, or may be printed on larger paper if you wish.
